file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: songs
  version: v1
components:
  securitySchemes:
    song_auth:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        implicit:
          authorizationUrl: http://localhost:8000/o/authorize
          scopes:
            read: read about a song
            create: create a new song
            update: update an existing song
            delete: delete a song
            post: create a new song
            widget: widget scope
            scope2: scope too
            scope3: another scope
paths:
  /songs:
    get:
      security:
        - song_auth: [read]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A list of songs.
    post:
      security:
        - song_auth: [create]
        - song_auth: [post, widget]
      responses:
        '201':
          description: new song added
    put:
      security:
        - song_auth: [update]
        - song_auth: [put, widget]
      responses:
        '204':
          description: song updated
    delete:
      security:
        - song_auth: [delete]
        - song_auth: [scope2, scope3]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: song deleted
